URL = http://english.sharehub.kr/


=Description=

"Share Hub is a project powered by Creative Commons Korea. Share Hub brings news and information related to sharing activities in Korea on ShareHub.kr. Share Hub also provides a directory of various sharing services and projects happening in Korea like a phone book for easy browsing on Korean sharing movement. Finally, Share Hub runs on and off line campaigns and seminars in order to raise awareness and engage general public participation on sharing. Especially, Share Hub is sponsored by Seoul City under “Seoul Metropolitan Government Act for Promoting Sharing.” This Act includes opening City Goverment data and contents, sharing municipally owned idle spaces, and supporting sharing economy services."


=More Information=

You can reach Share Hub at creative@cckorea.org.


